{
  "stem": "14168.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She worked for a little while for Bank of America, and then for one of the clothiers' firm here as a bookkeeper.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we had our second child, Leslie, who was born about 16 and 1/2 years after the birth of our first child.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Both children have made us very happy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then Ursula didn't have to work anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We moved to Westwood.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had lived in Hollywood for quite some time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she helped me make social arrangement, meet clients socially.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She worked for the community here, particularly in the public school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She was one of the direct-- for two terms, a director of the PTA of Uni High, and Emerson High before.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she had-- she also helped me with a program trying to give-- show hospitality to foreign visitors here in Los Angeles.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Not only, not limited only to my practice, but generally.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I then became also a-- I became the president of the Foreign Trade Association of Southern California.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I've been active in-- yes?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that was very interesting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because my first relationship was with a German Consulate General.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There, I had tremendous obstacles, emotional obstacles.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because right after the war, after we heard about what happened in Europe, we almost swore that we would never have-- want to have anything to do with Germans anymore.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Time went by, and in 1962, 1963, I was approached by a young attache to the German Consulate General here who had heard about me, knowing that I spoke German, whether they could recommend my services to people here, to Germans who needed American legal assistance, and whether they could also retain me as their lawyer.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I told him what my problem was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He said, I am of the young generation.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
